Pick Up Games Software
Major Objectives:
-Create Profile (name, location, stats, games created/joined, teams)
-Team Profile (name, home field/court, stats)
-Create games (possibly repeating)
-Add games to Google calender
-Search for games
-Join games found
-Show games by location (on a google map)
-Add teams (search for teams)
-Ranking system (played most, created most)
-Game types (free for all, team game)
-Auto create teams option (based on skill, stats, how often they play)
-Private match (invite-only, full control of teams, etc)

